title: Start with seven stunning senior sisters
description: Opening with seven beautiful sisters ,At the beginning, there are seven outstanding senior sisters,开局拥有七位绝色师姐, The Seven Beauties Are My Martial Sisters Description: Ye Chen was reborn in the Immortal Chance Holy Land on the Heavenly Mystery Continent and became the son of a peak leader. He had seven beautiful martial sisters, and they were proficient in different fields. After obtaining the powerful Check-in System, Ye Chen’s cultivation level skyrocketed. He quickly became a pillar of the Immortal Chance Holy Land and won the favor of his martial sisters. After helping the Immortal Chance Holy Land deal with various hostile sects, Ye Chen left the sect to seek justice for his martial sisters and gradually became the strongest person in the world.
